column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name],     p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,    dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,    p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, p.petror5#_r, p.petror9#_r  FROM #upload u       JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id       JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID  ORDER BY x.up_id
